MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2018-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 14th May, 2018
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 14th May, 2018:
(!
Shri Arun Jaitley relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance and the
charge of the office of the Minister of Corporate Affairs and assumed the charge of the
office of the Minister without Portfolio;
ii)
Smt. Smriti Zubin Irani relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Information
and Broadcasting. She will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of
Textiles;
Shri Piyush Goyal assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance and the
charge of the office of the Minister of Corporate Affairs temporarily. This arrangement will
be in vogue during the period of indisposition of Shri Arun Jaitley. Shri Piyush Goyal will
continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Railways and the charge of the
office of the Minister of Coal;
Col. Rajyavardhan Singh Rathore relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
State in the Ministry of Information and Broadcasting and assumed the charge of the
office of the Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Information and
Broadcasting. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of State
(Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Youth Affairs and Sports;
iv)
v)
Shri Alphons Kannanthanam relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State
in the Ministry of Electronics and Information Technology. He will continue to hold the
charge of the office of the Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of
Tourism; and
vi)
Shri S.S. Ahluwalia relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Drinking Water and Sanitation and assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of State in the Ministry of Electronics and Information Technology.
